                <p>Young Bankers Connect depends on an active and collective contribution. Joining Young Bankers, you will benefit from a wide network but the idea is also to expand that network by sharing it to your private network. The procedure is the same for the resources. Each member will benefit from them, but we also depend on your contribution to upload them and share your knowledge. Joining Young Bankers is also acquiring a recognition label with variable labels that each member will earn following his or her contribution.  <br /> </p>
                    <p>This page will explain how each one can contribute as well as what this association might bring you.  </p>
